  <brief_title>Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of MEDITOXIN in Treatment of Primary Axillary Hyperhidrosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo Controlled, Multi-Center Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of MEDITOXIN in Treatment of Primary Axillary Hyperhidrosis</official_title>
