  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult patients aged from 20 to 65, with persistent bilateral primary axillary
             hyperhidrosis

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  those who have secondary hyperhidrosis

          -  those who have systemic neuromuscular junction disorders

          -  women who are pregnant or lactating
      </textblock>
